title: La Tienda Organica - Comoconsentido
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Western, Juice bar, Fusion, Argentinian
description: Small restaurant with a section selling organic grocery items like dry beans, grains, nuts and oils. Menu has a tofu sandwich that is vegan, and a veggie sandwich with mayo (can be substituted for tahini). There are fresh juices, tea, some breakfast type meals. Est. 2015.
